Exclusion Criteria:

1. Severe hand spasticity or hand deformity;
2. History of alcohol or drug abuse or epilepsy;
3. Bilateral brain infarcts;
4. Severe cognitive deficits;
5. Comprehensive aphasia;
6. Contraindications to tDCS
